name: JinDwenDwen
description: The mascot of the 2022 Olympic Winter Games is the golden pier of Beijing. The panda image is combined with the super energy golden shell. The shape of the head shell is taken from the ice and snow sports helmet and decorated with a color halo. The overall image is similar to that of an astronaut. Jindundun means to create extraordinary and explore the future, reflecting the infinite possibility of pursuing excellence, leading the times and facing the future
